  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1934 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The leaflet features a framed graphic illustration of a man and woman. The man is wearing a broad-brimmed hat and has cartridge belts strapped across his shoulder and around his hips. He is carrying the woman in his arms. She is lying almost horizontally with her mouth open. The original film title is printed across the lower part of the image. Below to the right is the logo of film production company ‘Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer’.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was directed by Jack Conway and released in 1934.</ab>
